snippet.title: Helion: Void Wars - First trailer (MGW 2015)
snippet.description:
Helion: Void Wars is a 3D Spaceship combat game with strategic components, giving the player real time control over the battlefield. Done with Unreal engine 4 and a lot of love.

This trailer was made for the Madrid Games Week event and shows alpha footage of the game.

The team developing Helion:

Bytecore: http://www.bytecoregames.com/

Enjoy the official trailer of the next strategic spaceship battlefield and join us on our social media:

TWITTER:
http://www.twitter.com/BytecoreGames

FACEBOOK:
http://www.facebook.com/BytecoreGames
